          ],
          "SAMPLE": [
            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": null,
              "free_text": [
                ".Three Zr-90 targets with thicknesses of 485, 233 and",
                "  215-mg/cm**2 and a polyethylene-ch(2)-target with a",
                " thickness of 46-mg/cm**2 were mounted in a multiwire",
                " drift chamber."
              ]
            }
          ],
          "ADD-RES": [
            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": [
                "COMP"
              ],
              "free_text": [
                ".The distorted wave impulse approximation",
                " calculation. Multipole decomposition analysis.",
                " The  Gamow-Teller (GT) quenching q-factor was derived",
                " by using the obtained total GT-strengths. The result",
                " is q=0.88+-0.06 not including an overall normalization",
                " uncertainty in the gt-unit cross section of 16%."
              ]
            }
          ],
          "FACILITY": [
            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": {
                "facility": [
                  "ACCEL"
                ],
                "institute": "2JPNOSA"
              },
              "free_text": [
                "  Large acceptance spectrometer."
              ]
            }
          ],
          "INC-SOURCE": [
            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": {
                "incident_source": [
                  "P-LI7"
                ],
                "reaction": null
              },
              "free_text": [
                " The primary proton beam, after going through",
                " the Li-7 target, was deflected away by the clearing",
                " magnet to a faraday cup in the floor. The typical",
                " beam intensity was 450-Na and thickness of the Li-7",
                " target was 320-mg/cm**2."
              ]
            }
          ],
          "INC-SPECT": [
            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": null,
              "free_text": [
                " *En-rsl*.The overall energy resolution is 1.5-MeV,",
                "  mainly originating from the target thicknesses and",
                "  the energy spread of the beam."
              ]
            }
          ],
